s of AACS and BD+. No one has the license to this app, making it free for everyone. Additionally, this means that it works on most systems.","The decision of which software is the solution for you comes down to whether you are looking for a free solution with substantial quality or don t mind paying a few bucks to get more options, such as higher ripping speed and superior playback quality. There s no point paying for features you won t use, and many of the free software programs cover most ripping needs."]},"id":"8b3410e9-08ca-4233-a504-d42815535ad6","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_9752","url":"/best-rippers-for-mac","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"top-ten-reviews-contributor","url":"/author/top-ten-reviews-contributor","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Top Ten Reviews Contributor","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"w5zRTt8zKNM8ERYhxFTX9","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-08-05T19:10:13Z","datePublished":"2015-08-05T19:10:13Z","name":"The Five Best DVD Rippers for Mac","synopsis":"Whether you’re going on a trip and want the ease of watching movies from your MacBook or are just looking for a way to back up some of your favorite movies, DVD rippers make storing DVD content on you","review":{},"strapline":"Whether you’re going on a trip and want the ease of watching movies from your MacBook or are just looking for a way to back up some of your favorite movies, DVD rippers make storing DVD content on you","language":"en","dateModified":"2015-08-05T19:18:06Z","id":"x3LmX64Q7E4XuQPkJkQUd6","meta":{"title":"The Five Best DVD Rippers for Mac","description":"Visit Top Ten Reviews to read the latest reviews and opinions. Reviews are complete with product ratings and comparisons."},"products":[],"dateImported":"2019-04-17T21:07:35Z","type":"feature","template":"standard","social":{"twitter":{"image":{"status":"","height":0,"path":"/qjjbNbQcXfjcYAbzqRpZTi.jpg","chec